      ✅ Answer: b. Obtuse angleExplanation: Poor wetting corresponds to a large contact angle (&gt;90°), which is obtuse. Good wetting occurs when the angle is small (&lt;90°).解析： 液體不潤濕固體表面時，接觸角大於90°，屬於鈍角；良好潤濕時接觸角小於90°。




