      ✅ Answer: All of the above (a, b, c, d)Explanation: PCL has lower Tg and Tm, making it easier to process; it degrades slowly, providing long-term support, and has superior mechanical strength compared to PLGA.解析： PCL玻璃轉化溫度和熔點低，易加工；降解時間長，能長期支撐；機械強度高於PLGA，適合顱骨再生。




